name: A Trip To Lost Valley
description: The Lost Valley trail is a unique one in its own beauty. Nested away between hills, it has this feeling of peacefulness upon itself. At the end of the trail is this waterfall flowing out from a cave system that has a long history of being of being used for shelter by humans under different circumstances. And at the time of when I took this, it provided me with a shelter of peace while I was going through a rough time in my life.
